<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_fdd97b44-089b-4147-a55f-602834a71e8c" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="TAS"><sptc>C4P2</sptc><title id="_c670ba37-c962-4230-9440-bf85b479c67f">Transferal of liquid trade waste</title><archive-num>2019: Tas HP2.2</archive-num><subclause id="_5d85e49d-f1a4-4c35-88b3-79ba94c4bb3c" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_58c00e2d-e9d2-4677-a39d-c42db7fa2299">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Liquid trade waste must be transferred within the disposal system and treatment devices in a way that avoids—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_297a5162-547c-4cbb-a5a2-a67c1277e572"><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1209_1.2.0.xml#_417d94d8-f254-4788-9a14-c4c5da89daa6" id="_eee90fe1-4cf4-4bd2-8b28-371f304baf9f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">blockage</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1500_27.0.0.xml#_0ece1af9-d663-4f17-a7c9-bf59ebb1b1ef" id="_a4f41851-05b0-4024-9d57-2bb50dcc4f80" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">uncontrolled discharge</xref>: and</li><li id="_00922889-a405-4041-b018-fe2a9ac3259d">the entry of foul air and gasses into buildings.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_9549ca00-170d-4979-a99f-8d2f0f280c5a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_2eb44464-4864-427c-9aa6-f2450a82f649">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Liquid trade waste must be transferred within the disposal system and treatment devices in a way that ensures—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_b965a49b-3681-4958-8029-ed504f2221ef">the safe and hygienic transferal of waste; and</li><li id="_069a0133-8af8-414a-bdcc-2a7dcfd7896f">safe access for clearing <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1209_1.2.0.xml#_417d94d8-f254-4788-9a14-c4c5da89daa6" id="_90020b6a-3ec8-4161-8efd-06afc01f4e5d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">blockages</xref>.</li></ol></subclause></clause>